#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Rapports"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Reports View is a tabbed display. The <guilabel>Reports</guilabel> tab "
"is always displayed, and lists all available reports, grouped under the "
"headings listed and described below. You can click <quote>></quote> to "
"expand or collapse the specific reports under each heading. When you open "
"any report, it is displayed in an additional tab, labelled with the name of "
"that report."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of reports is always sorted first by the group name (by number) and "
"then by report name. Clicking the <quote>Reports</quote> heading will "
"reverse the sort order. You can also click the <quote>Comment</quote> header "
"to sort by the report comment instead of name. The report's name and comment "
"can be set or edited on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab of the <link "
"linkend=\"details.reports.config\">Report Configuration</link> dialog."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Reports"
msgstr "Rapports disponibles"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:32
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
